<%= render "mailers/shared/header",
    title: "Your New #{@pillar_name} Strategy is Ready",
    company_name: "My Custom Sleep Journey" %>

<div style="padding: 0 30px 20px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">

  <p>
    Dear <strong><%= @user.last_name %></strong>,
  </p>

  <p>
    Your coach has just published a new tailored strategy within your
    <strong><%= @pillar_name %></strong> module.
  </p>

  <p>
    We know your shift schedule is demanding, so this plan has been specifically
    designed to integrate into your upcoming routine without adding unnecessary stress.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">
    What’s inside your updated plan:
  </p>

  <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>
      <strong>Targeted Actions:</strong>
      Specific steps for your next 24–48 hours.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Biometric Focus:</strong>
      How this plan will help stabilize your Oura scores.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Adherence Requirements:</strong>
      Details on the proof you’ll need to upload to stay on track.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <strong>Next Step:</strong><br>
    Please log in to the Custom Sleep Journey dashboard to review the instructions
    and prepare for your next shift.
  </p>

  <%= render "mailers/shared/button",
      text: "View My New Plan",
      url: @dashboard_url %>

  <p style="margin-top: 25px;">
    To your health and recovery,<br>
    <strong style="color:#0e3264;">The My Custom Sleep Journey Team</strong>
  </p>

</div>

<%= render "mailers/shared/footer",
    note: "This email was sent to #{@user.email}",
    company_name: "My Custom Sleep Journey" %>
